Efficacy and Safety of the mRNA-1273 #SARSCoV2 #Vaccine

The mRNA-1273 vaccine showed 94.1% efficacy at preventing #COVID19 illness, including severe disease. Aside from transient local and systemic reactions, no safety concerns were identified.
